<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9800, #ffb74d);
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        background: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .alert {
        background: #fff3cd;
        border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
        color: #856404;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .info-box {
        background: #e3f2fd;
        border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: #666;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>⚠️ KRA Returned for L1 Review</h1>
      <h2><%= @quarter %> Quarter - <%= @employee.employee_name %></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear L1 Manager,</p>

      <div class="alert">
        <strong>The <%= @quarter %> Quarter KRA for <%= @employee.employee_name %> has been returned by L2 Manager for your review.</strong>
      </div>

      <p>L2 Manager has reviewed the quarterly achievements and has returned them to you for further review and action. Please review the L2 feedback and take appropriate action.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>📋 Employee Details:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Employee:</strong> <%= @employee.employee_name %></li>
          <li><strong>Employee Code:</strong> <%= @employee.employee_code %></li>
          <li><strong>Quarter:</strong> <%= @quarter %></li>
          <li><strong>Department:</strong> <%= @employee.department_name %></li>
          <li><strong>L1 Manager:</strong> <%= @employee.l1_employer_name %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
      <ol>
        <li>Log into the KRA system</li>
        <li>Review the L2 feedback and remarks</li>
        <li>Review the employee's achievements</li>
        <li>Take appropriate action (approve, return to employee, or provide additional feedback)</li>
      </ol>

      <p>Please ensure timely review and action to maintain the KRA process flow.</p>

      <p>If you have any questions, please contact the L2 Manager or HR department.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>
      KRA Management System</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message from the KRA Management System.</p>
      <p>Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
